com.ryhma6.maven.steambeater.model.steamAPI

Class GameStatistics

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ryhma6.maven.steambeater.model.steamAPI.GameStatistics

  • public class GameStatistics
extends java.lang.Object
    Object model of the player's game statistics (including list of achievements) parsed from SteamAPI JSON. SteamAPI documentation: https://developer.valvesoftware.com/wiki/Steam_Web_API
